1
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:20,940
=About Love=

2
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 20=

3
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:25,480
Mom.

4
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:29,350
I'm bringing my boyfriend Bei to see you

5
00:01:29,350 --> 00:01:30,350
in a couple of days.

6
00:01:30,510 --> 00:01:31,590
Get ready.

7
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:34,350
I've been waiting for this day.

8
00:01:34,590 --> 00:01:37,200
I'm curious what kind of guy

9
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:39,510
could make my picky daughter
so satisfied.

10
00:01:39,790 --> 00:01:41,150
I'm not picky.

11
00:01:41,150 --> 00:01:42,400
Don't make it sound like that.

12
00:01:42,950 --> 00:01:45,590
Not picky? You've been single for years.

13
00:01:46,340 --> 00:01:47,200
By the way,

14
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,560
your dad happens to be heading your way.

15
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,590
I asked your dad to check him out first.

16
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:51,760
Dad's here?

17
00:01:52,790 --> 00:01:53,950
When did he arrive?

18
00:01:54,230 --> 00:01:55,430
Why didn't he call me?

19
00:01:55,710 --> 00:01:56,840
He's on a business trip.

20
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,200
I told him to stop by after he's done.

21
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:01,040
Didn't tell you in advance
because I didn't want you to worry.

22
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,870
Didn't want to trouble you.

23
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:21,150
Jiang Yifan is Jiang Yifan.

24
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:24,770
Jiang Yifan will never be Li Xiaoxi.

25
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:26,910
What I liked
was just a made-up character.

26
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,800
Mm, got it.

27
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:38,080
Alright, hanging up. Bye bye.

28
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:40,960
What's wrong? A call from home?

29
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,800
Mm.

30
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,590
Mom said my dad's here

31
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:45,870
on a business trip.

32
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,280
I asked him to dinner tomorrow night.

33
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,240
You coming?

34
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,190
Of course.

35
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:52,280
Why don't I book the restaurant?

36
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,800
What does your dad like to eat?

37
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:55,800
How about...

38
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,750
Sichuan food?

39
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,640
Forget it.

40
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,240
Your family always eats Sichuan food.

41
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,080
- You're...
- Western...

42
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,910
Are you feeling a bit nervous?

43
00:03:02,910 --> 00:03:05,120
Me? Nervous about what? I'm not nervous.

44
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:05,960
Where's my phone?

45
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,870
I'm not nervous.

46
00:03:06,870 --> 00:03:08,590
You're nervous. You are.

47
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:10,520
I'm not. Why would I be nervous?

48
00:03:10,870 --> 00:03:12,000
Wait, my phone's here.

49
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,150
So…

50
00:03:13,150 --> 00:03:14,360
When's your dad heading back?

51
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,560
Should I prepare something?

52
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,960
Going back with your dad,

53
00:03:17,150 --> 00:03:18,150
and meet aunt then.

54
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:20,120
Just say hello.

55
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:20,960
What's the rush?

56
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,470
I'm not rushing.

57
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:25,000
You're in such a hurry.
I need to think carefully.

58
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,870
Should I think it over some more?

59
00:03:27,910 --> 00:03:29,520
You really should.

60
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:30,710
I'll give you three seconds.

61
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,590
Three, two...

62
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:33,800
Okay!

63
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,080
That was fast.

64
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,910
You really thought hard about it.

65
00:03:44,030 --> 00:03:45,910
Since you've thought it through
so carefully,

66
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,800
promise me one thing.

67
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:49,960
What is it?

68
00:03:54,030 --> 00:03:55,000
Don't leave me.

69
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,080
I promise.

70
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,200
Deal.

71
00:04:22,950 --> 00:04:25,720
We used to drink like this all the time.

72
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,920
Why did we break up?

73
00:04:33,430 --> 00:04:35,190
How much did you drink already?

74
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,630
Don't play dumb
just because you're tipsy.

75
00:04:42,270 --> 00:04:43,600
Well, I...

76
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:48,160
liked you so, so much.

77
00:04:49,950 --> 00:04:52,070
Why would I leave you?

78
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:55,270
Because I'm a jerk.

79
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,830
I fell for someone else.

80
00:04:58,390 --> 00:04:59,270
That's not true.

81
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:01,110
I know

82
00:05:02,270 --> 00:05:04,310
you're mad at me.

83
00:05:05,310 --> 00:05:07,720
Mad because I don't trust you.

84
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:11,160
And even had someone test you.

85
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:17,120
So you knew all along?

86
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:20,510
It's one of the reasons.

87
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,600
I didn't want to.

88
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,070
But I…

89
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,830
When I started thinking about

90
00:05:31,830 --> 00:05:33,160
how many women

91
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,830
you might be chatting with
on your phone,

92
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:36,560
I just couldn't help it.

93
00:05:39,750 --> 00:05:42,630
If you like me, can't you stay loyal?

94
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:46,430
Do you remember what you told me before?

95
00:05:47,310 --> 00:05:48,310
You said,

96
00:05:49,430 --> 00:05:50,360
"Yu He,

97
00:05:50,950 --> 00:05:51,790
don't worry.

98
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,240
I'll never hurt you."

99
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,360
Total nonsense.

100
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,360
In this world,

101
00:06:03,190 --> 00:06:04,680
the one who hurt me the most

102
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:08,350
is you.

103
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,310
To...

104
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,630
stop hurting you,

105
00:06:23,310 --> 00:06:24,560
so I left.

106
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:26,950
How could you say

107
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:29,000
something so awful?

108
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:32,510
You shouldn't have come to me
in the first place.

109
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:47,190
Back when we first got together,

110
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,310
you were like a doll.

111
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:55,830
More like an angel.

112
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,950
You had wings.

113
00:07:01,190 --> 00:07:02,720
You loved circling around me,

114
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,200
hovering here

115
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,320
and there.

116
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,750
But as time went on,

117
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,480
those wings disappeared.

118
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,800
Knew there'd be a catch.

119
00:07:44,190 --> 00:07:45,120
You'd

120
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:48,870
always cling to my arm

121
00:07:49,830 --> 00:07:50,670
and my leg.

122
00:07:51,190 --> 00:07:52,750
Sometimes you cling onto my back

123
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,360
like a koala,

124
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:58,270
weighing me down

125
00:07:59,630 --> 00:08:02,310
heavier and heavier,

126
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,830
until I can barely breathe.

127
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:04,670
Let me see.

128
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:06,920
What's there to see? Are you a kid?

129
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:07,870
Let me take a look.

130
00:08:07,870 --> 00:08:08,830
Am I your girlfriend

131
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:10,190
or is she?

132
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:11,030
What right does she have?

133
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,630
If I tried to put you down,

134
00:08:13,190 --> 00:08:14,120
or

135
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:17,360
tried to talk to other women,

136
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:18,750
you'd let out

137
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,950
shrill screams.

138
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,070
Do you dislike me that much?

139
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,360
It's not that I dislike you.

140
00:08:30,750 --> 00:08:32,030
I just feel

141
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:35,870
a bit tired.

142
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:42,030
I just joked with your bestie,

143
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:43,150
and you got mad about it.

144
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:46,000
You even suspected something
between me and Luanluan.

145
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:52,240
Am I not allowed to have female friends?

146
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,480
You went out of your way,

147
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:56,030
racked your brain

148
00:08:56,510 --> 00:08:59,240
to find proof that I was unfaithful.

149
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,120
Did you find any?

150
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,120
Congrats,

151
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,320
you finally succeeded.

152
00:09:15,270 --> 00:09:16,270
But...

153
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,360
when you like someone,

154
00:09:21,910 --> 00:09:23,360
you just get insecure.

155
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:28,440
If you think Li Xiaoxi's great,

156
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:30,440
then go be with her.

157
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:32,960
See if you don't drive her nuts.

158
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:35,630
Wait.

159
00:09:35,790 --> 00:09:36,840
Wait, that's not right.

160
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,720
She doesn't even like you.

161
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,870
She doesn't even care

162
00:09:45,150 --> 00:09:45,990
how many

163
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:48,720
close female friends you have.

164
00:09:54,270 --> 00:09:55,670
Enough.

165
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:58,360
She's getting married. Why bring her up?

166
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,120
Wait.

167
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:05,630
She's marrying Bei?

168
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,870
That fast?

169
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:13,390
Thank goodness.

170
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,000
Thank goodness.

171
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,150
Lucky she didn't end up with you.

172
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:17,990
Otherwise,

173
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:21,960
she'd never have gotten a happy ending.

174
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,960
Are you here to insult me?

175
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:33,270
You told me they're getting married.

176
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,910
Struck a nerve, huh?

177
00:10:40,030 --> 00:10:41,870
Yeah, I am here to insult you.

178
00:10:43,030 --> 00:10:44,720
And I'm gonna scold you.

179
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:48,670
I dislike you, hate you,

180
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:50,240
and resent you.

181
00:10:51,390 --> 00:10:53,870
I'll do whatever it takes
to get back at you.

182
00:10:53,870 --> 00:10:55,790
I want you

183
00:10:55,790 --> 00:10:57,840
to never be with someone you like.

184
00:11:03,150 --> 00:11:04,670
I can't stop thinking about you.

185
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,200
What's wrong?

186
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:44,870
I don't want to hurt you again.

187
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,120
Are you afraid I'll cling to you?

188
00:11:54,390 --> 00:11:56,360
Actually, I was about to...

189
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,440
get married.

190
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:05,110
Well...

191
00:12:06,790 --> 00:12:07,630
You...

192
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,750
Did you take me as

193
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:11,440
your last wild night before marriage?

194
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,560
I...

195
00:12:15,790 --> 00:12:18,240
I follow the rules and have principles.

196
00:12:18,550 --> 00:12:19,440
I'm a decent person.

197
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:32,720
Let me tell you, I've

198
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:35,120
imagined so many times

199
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,320
how you'd react

200
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,550
when you heard the news.

201
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:40,000
Would you be even a little

202
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:43,720
bit sad?

203
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,270
Or

204
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:46,390
regretful?

205
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,200
Thanks.

206
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:53,510
Thanks for letting me know
I was overthinking.

207
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:58,870
Congrats.

208
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:01,750
That guy

209
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:03,670
must be more reliable than me.

210
00:13:05,390 --> 00:13:06,230
T...

211
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:08,320
Today's full of good news.

212
00:13:08,810 --> 00:13:09,750
Just pretend it didn't...

213
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:12,200
He discussed home renovation with me

214
00:13:13,030 --> 00:13:14,670
and brainstormed

215
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:16,840
baby names with me.

216
00:13:17,550 --> 00:13:19,750
He made so many plans

217
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:20,960
for the future with me.

218
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:24,120
You must think it's silly.

219
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:28,080
Because you never talk to me about that.

220
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:31,120
In your future,

221
00:13:33,150 --> 00:13:34,480
I'm nowhere to be found.

222
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,510
You know me.

223
00:13:41,720 --> 00:13:43,750
I live for the moment.

224
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:48,120
When he proposed to me,

225
00:13:49,630 --> 00:13:51,550
all I could think about was you.

226
00:13:53,030 --> 00:13:54,720
I just wanted you to know

227
00:13:55,910 --> 00:13:58,360
someone wanted to marry me.

228
00:13:59,910 --> 00:14:01,150
But then I backed out.

229
00:14:03,510 --> 00:14:04,720
I got scared again.

230
00:14:07,390 --> 00:14:10,080
I was wondering if I was really
ready to marry this person.

231
00:14:14,270 --> 00:14:15,360
I wasn't sure.

232
00:14:16,630 --> 00:14:19,080
I couldn't marry him
with that thought in my heart.

233
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,030
So I told him

234
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,910
I still haven't completely let you go.

235
00:14:24,220 --> 00:14:26,260
♪I'll stay insane♪

236
00:14:26,620 --> 00:14:29,290
♪When you call my name♪

237
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:31,910
I came today
because I wanted to see you.

238
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:35,120
Until the moment
you were getting out of the car,

239
00:14:35,120 --> 00:14:36,840
I still didn't know
how to start talking.

240
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:40,910
But luckily,

241
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:43,670
luckily you mentioned

242
00:14:43,670 --> 00:14:46,030
the comic adaptation.

243
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,120
You have no idea

244
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,790
how happy I was

245
00:14:50,510 --> 00:14:51,600
in that moment.

246
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:55,330
It's all in the past.

247
00:14:55,330 --> 00:14:57,000
♪At night♪

248
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:59,880
♪I wonder if it will go away♪

249
00:15:00,030 --> 00:15:01,390
Is there any chance for us?

250
00:15:02,970 --> 00:15:04,710
♪At dawn♪

251
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:07,720
I'm...

252
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,270
still that jerk.

253
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,870
We can't make the same mistake twice.

254
00:15:18,130 --> 00:15:21,500
♪Thinking about how to stay the same♪

255
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:23,550
The second time isn't a mistake.

256
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:27,150
It's a choice.

257
00:15:27,150 --> 00:15:31,980
♪I lie awake♪

258
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,480
I already know what you've chosen.

259
00:15:34,180 --> 00:15:37,860
♪Thinking there's nothing I could say♪

260
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:42,310
♪Only to lie and lie awake♪

261
00:15:43,670 --> 00:15:44,600
I'm sorry.

262
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:49,480
I never meant to hurt you.

263
00:15:51,030 --> 00:15:51,870
You know what?

264
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:03,960
Yu He.

265
00:16:16,890 --> 00:16:18,860
♪At night♪

266
00:16:19,030 --> 00:16:23,630
♪I wonder if it will go away♪

267
00:16:24,690 --> 00:16:26,970
♪At dawn♪

268
00:16:26,970 --> 00:16:31,620
♪I wonder if I will be okay♪

269
00:16:32,860 --> 00:16:39,860
♪I lie awake♪

270
00:16:40,140 --> 00:16:44,060
♪Thinking there's nothing I could say♪

271
00:16:44,230 --> 00:16:48,550
♪Only to lie and lie awake♪

272
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,080
What's this?

273
00:16:56,270 --> 00:16:57,440
It's a music box.

274
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:59,320
It's the little princess.

275
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:02,870
It's a dancing little princess.

276
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:04,640
Do you like it?

277
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:05,720
I do.

278
00:17:06,070 --> 00:17:07,310
Thank you, Dad.

279
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:11,880
It's really beautiful.

280
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:17,480
No.

281
00:17:17,790 --> 00:17:18,960
He's not your dad.

282
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:20,480
He's not.

283
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:50,270
(Uncle)
(Sen)

284
00:17:50,270 --> 00:17:52,110
(Can you stop worrying the family?)

285
00:17:52,350 --> 00:17:53,680
(Break up with her.)

286
00:17:54,340 --> 00:17:56,540
(Aunt)

287
00:17:57,110 --> 00:17:58,310
(Text)
(Have you lost your mind?)

288
00:17:58,440 --> 00:17:59,960
(She's a homewrecker.)

289
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:01,160
(And you still want to be with her?)

290
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:02,550
(Take my advice.)

291
00:18:02,830 --> 00:18:03,880
