301
00:19:40,270 --> 00:19:41,750
And got back in bed out of habit.

302
00:19:42,510 --> 00:19:43,400
I forgot you were here.

303
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:45,000
It's okay.

304
00:19:45,590 --> 00:19:46,790
Why so formal with me?

305
00:19:53,270 --> 00:19:54,110
We...

306
