311
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:21,790
Thinking about when we were together?

312
00:20:24,270 --> 00:20:25,400
I was wondering

313
00:20:27,510 --> 00:20:29,680
if your boyfriend's gonna
show up and take me out.

314
